data.description: EXTREMLEY RARE OPPORTUNITY! Nestled on the north shore of Liberty Lake with sandy beach & private dock, this 3 bed/3 bath waterfront home with an attached shop and stunning views is everything you've been searching for! The open-concept living area has gorgeous lake views, vaulted ceilings, and is ready for your updating ideas. The location is arguably the best on Liberty Lake, is Southern facing for lots of natural light & sun, has a gently sloping sandy beach, and 3 golf courses within minutes - 1 just 3 blocks away! This home is such a rarity to have North Shore sandy, flat frontage with a huge attached shop that can house 4+ cars & has tons of storage space. Also includes a huge 2 car carport, and possibilities for additional bedrooms. You will also find a workshop, fenced area, dock, and your own private sandy beach! Such a true gem you won't want to miss out on!
